{"tid":348503,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"不如組織一個點鳩無禮貌支那人活動","createTime":"2017-08-05T18:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T19:10:42.000Z","uid":4322,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2ab77a782908c43d02663e36b7715480434763","tid":348503,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T18:02:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的 剛剛睇完呢個post 有感而發<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，頭先指左個大陸佬兜大圈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347627/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347627/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n為左等佢地知道路唔是咁問的<br />\n諗緊不如組織一個點鳩無禮貌支那人既活動 <br />\n好撚多支那人問路好似老奉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如就點鳩佢地(佢地老母)錯路/搭錯車<br />\n去荃灣就點佢過海去柴灣 <br />\n(記得一定要搭巴士！ <br />\n因為地鐵太多指示太清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n等佢地認識下香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋有無得整合一個表<br />\n例如等佢地本身想荃灣 <br />\n點撚佢地搭程巴士去左柴灣咁撚樣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f727dae0714d7c0bb83e531f5b2f07437af77545","tid":348503,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T18:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的 剛剛睇完呢個post 有感而發<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，頭先指左個大陸佬兜大圈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347627/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347627/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n為左等佢地知道路唔是咁問的<br />\n諗緊不如組織一個點鳩無禮貌支那人既活動 <br />\n好